flexflux.interaction

Class Unique

  • java.lang.Object
    • flexflux.interaction.Relation
      • flexflux.interaction.Unique
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UndeterminedUnique

    public class Unique
extends Relation
    This class represents a Unique relation.

    This type of relation doesn't contain any other relation and is the end of a branch.

    It contains an entity, a value and an operation.

    Author:
    lmarmiesse 7 mars 2013
